---
// src/pages/terms.astro
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Terms & Conditions - WinBet"
  description="Read WinBet's terms and conditions for using our online casino and slots platform. Understand your rights and responsibilities as a user."
>
  <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6 text-[#ffd700]">Terms & Conditions</h1>
    <div class="space-y-6 text-lg">
      <p>
        Welcome to WinBet. By accessing or using our website, you agree to
        comply with and be bound by the following Terms & Conditions. Please
        read these carefully.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        1. Eligibility to Use the Site
      </h2>
      <p>
        The Site is exclusively intended for residents of Madagascar who are of
        legal age to participate in gaming activities, typically 18 years or
        older. By registering and using the Site, you confirm that you meet
        these requirements.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        2. Account Registration and Responsibility
      </h2>
      <p>
        Users are permitted to hold only one account on the Site. Accounts are
        for personal use only and are non-transferable. You are solely
        responsible for all activities conducted under your account.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        3. User Responsibility and Compliance
      </h2>
      <p>
        You are responsible for ensuring your participation on the Site complies
        with all local laws. The Site does not guarantee that its services are
        lawful in all jurisdictions.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        4. No Know Your Customer (KYC) Verification
      </h2>
      <p>
        Currently, the Site does not implement a KYC process. The Site reserves
        the right to introduce KYC verification in the future if deemed
        necessary for security or compliance.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        5. Game Availability and Results
      </h2>
      <p>
        The Site provides access to online slots games powered by random number
        generators (RNG). All game outcomes are final and cannot be disputed.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        6. Betting and Wagering
      </h2>
      <p>
        All bets placed on the Site are final. Users should review their bets
        before confirming. Misunderstandings of game rules or accidental wagers
        are non-refundable.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        7. Account Management and Fund Handling
      </h2>
      <p>
        Withdrawals and deposits may be subject to minimum and maximum
        thresholds. The Site reserves the right to delay or refuse withdrawals
        in cases of suspected fraud or misuse.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        8. Responsible Gaming
      </h2>
      <p>
        The Site encourages responsible gaming practices. Currently, there are
        no self-exclusion or account restrictions available due to local
        regulatory limitations.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        9. Prohibited Conduct
      </h2>
      <p>
        Users are prohibited from engaging in fraudulent activities, using the
        Site for money laundering, and attempting to manipulate game outcomes.
        Violations may result in account termination.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        10. Privacy and Data Handling
      </h2>
      <p>
        The Site collects only essential registration information and respects
        user privacy. Data will not be shared with third parties except as
        required by law.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        11. Liability and Disclaimer
      </h2>
      <p>
        The Site is provided "as is" and without warranties. The Site is not
        liable for losses due to technical failures, unauthorized access, or
        misuse of the platform.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        12. Modifications to the Terms
      </h2>
      <p>
        The Site reserves the right to modify these Terms at any time without
        notice. Continued use of the Site after changes indicates acceptance of
        the new Terms.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        13. Governing Law and Jurisdiction
      </h2>
      <p>
        These Terms are governed by the laws of Madagascar, with disputes
        subject to its courts. Any unenforceable portion of these Terms does not
        affect the remainder.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        14. Account Termination
      </h2>
      <p>
        Users may request account closure at any time. The Site reserves the
        right to terminate any account violating these Terms or engaged in
        fraudulent activity.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4 text-[#ffd700]">
        15. Acceptance of Terms
      </h2>
      <p>
        By using the Site, you acknowledge and agree to these Terms &
        Conditions. Continued use signifies acceptance of updates to these
        Terms.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
